{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act18d3", "eventName": "覆潮之下", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SV-9", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "篤信者", "storyInfo": "三名獵人獵殺了主教變成的怪物。她們一路對付著小海怪，一齊衝出教堂。在教堂門外，她們遇到了一個意想不到的人。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibcave"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "殘垣斷壁裡，怪物將死的臃腫肉體填塞了大半個溶洞。它原本不斷散發出奇異之美的古怪軀體因它對死亡的畏懼而愈顯僵硬。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "四處都在漏水。了結它，我們得走了。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼你們這種瞎了眼睛的庸人能苟活？為什麼我這樣為事業投入了生命，專注於偉大目標的人......會失敗？", "name": "主教？"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盲目、停止流動的阿戈爾拴著的寵物......你們對科學和未來......毫無助益！", "name": "主教？"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已......幾近真理！為什麼我要死在這裡？！而你們......卻能逃脫你們應得的酷刑？", "name": "主教？"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我走了這麼遠，我的意志和肉體，都快要撕碎人類軀殼的束縛了！為什麼？", "name": "主教？"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼？為什麼？！為什麼！！", "name": "主教？"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閉嘴。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "主教？"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿戈爾......必定毀滅。你們什麼都不剩......什麼都......", "name": "主教？"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蠢材。我活著，我就是阿戈爾，我活著，阿戈爾就活著。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你......但......", "name": "主教？"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諷刺......諷刺。", "name": "主教？"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是不一樣的。呼......你註定不同......", "name": "主教？"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很清楚。你的命運已定。", "name": "主教？"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要再廢話連篇了。請你乖乖死掉，對你我只剩下這個請求。我很真誠的。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我詛咒你們......我要詛咒你們......直到陸地被淹沒......你們會像鹽粒一樣，逃出大海......最後還是被大海溶解。", "name": "主教？"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你們屍骨堆砌的貧瘠荒原上，我們鼓動不歇的潮聲會在蒼白夜空下浸沒大陸！", "name": "主教？"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "歌蕾蒂婭似乎在克制。她最後一點禮貌來自她白淨面容藏不住的厭惡。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "嗚咽般的喉聲自主教伸向歌蕾蒂婭的觸肢裡傳來。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但在觸及獵人前，這條觸肢就已經僵化，抽搐，蜷縮成一團。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "主教死去了。他的一切都將被遺忘。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "歌蕾蒂婭看著幽靈鯊和斯卡蒂。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "ac18_12_1", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xTo": 30.0, "duration": 25.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"faddetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_143_ghost#2"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總算死了。這事情也算是結束了......我親手殺了它。沒我想像裡那樣令人高興。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "char_143_ghost#2"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起他們對我做的這些，真是太輕了。殺了一個，還有兩個。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "char_143_ghost#2"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，頭又有點暈了。我是怎麼過來的？簡直就像一直在做夢。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "char_143_ghost#2"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鯊魚？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_143_ghost#2"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟......沒法一直醒著。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "char_143_ghost#2"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們抓到了他們的觸手，現在順著摸過去，把他們連根拔起，一定能找到治好你的辦法。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_143_ghost#2"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事。現在它們控制不了我，我感覺很好。自由的感覺......竟然是在這時候。我快飄起來了。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "char_143_ghost#2"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_143_ghost#2"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，隊長，你們說的我都聽到了。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "char_143_ghost#2"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它是說我們也會變成海嗣？隊長，你會變成特別厲害的那種？還挺強的。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "char_143_ghost#2"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會的。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你和它們可太不一樣了。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望我沒有因為自己的獨斷專行而害了你們。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回答我幾個問題。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有問必答。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們體內流著海嗣的血？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你來這裡是為了確認幽靈鯊身體問題的原因。你之所以要吃那一下是為了知道為什麼海嗣想找我。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你早就知道這裡不止主教一隻海嗣？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道我們那場自殺一樣的決戰的最後，我做了什麼嗎？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們贏了嗎？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不知道。我與阿戈爾失去了聯繫。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我們是不是阿戈爾的棄子？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "是？深海獵人就像誘餌。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "是？深海獵人就像海底的光亮。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "是？深海獵人的力量這樣巨大，卻只是阿戈爾的萬分之一。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "是？深海獵人的特殊，只在於他們的確和海怪有聯繫。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "怒火在斯卡蒂紅色的瞳孔裡打轉，但那一點點希望......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "多少是真話，多少是謊言......？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "ac18_12_2", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行了。走吧。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_143_ghost#2"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真爽快。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "char_143_ghost#2"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒什麼好磨蹭的。我畢竟是個深海獵人。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......難道二隊的人不這樣？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#4"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深海獵人都這樣。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#4"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡快塌了，而且......", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#8"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tense_intro", "key": "$tense_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "彷彿被主教的屍體所吸引，恐魚們從溶洞的裂口處鑽了進來。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "密密麻麻。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "三個獵人走上海岸♪", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_143_ghost#3"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibcoastd"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘁，太多了。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "char_143_ghost#3"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂！拿出點力氣來！這裡就只剩你胳膊腿都沒破皮了！", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "char_143_ghost#3"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還要怎樣......我手都撕麻了。你上次用手伸進它們的嘴把它們撕成兩半是什麼時候？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三秒前。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "歌蕾蒂婭猛地回轉身子，將手自一隻怪物的口器刺入，從頭至足將它刺穿。她急速揮動手臂，小怪物身體承受不住獵人的力量，被獵人活活從體內破開，飛了出去。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行。只要那具身體還在那......恐魚就不會停。它在呼喚它們。那是個錨！", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_143_ghost#3"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "得毀掉那具屍體才行......填埋可不夠......", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "char_143_ghost#3"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_143_ghost#2"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就憑你這破了個大洞的身子？", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "char_143_ghost#2"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們可以——", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "一個身影出現在獵人們眼前，斯卡蒂看到了她的臉，不禁驚呼。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獵人們，快走！", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼是你？！", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之後再說！Mon3tr，去！", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "Mon3tr衝向了教堂頂部，恐魚在它的利刃前飛散，它自口部凝聚出一個黑色的球體，向教堂下方吐去。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "整座城市地動山搖。教堂崩塌了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "主教和它的秘密被永遠地毀滅了。沒人想知道。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}